==Esperanto==
===Etymology===
Esperanto ''[[ki-]]'' (interrogative and relative [[:Category:Esperanto correlatives|correlative]] prefix) + ''[[-am]]'' (correlative suffix of time)

===Correlative===
'''kiam'''
# [[when]] (interrogative and relative correlative of time)
#: Like other interrogative and relative correlatives, '''kiam''' can be combined with ''[[ajn]]'', the adverbial particle of generality. '''''Kiam''' ajn'' thus means ''[[whenever]]''.

